    </x-slot>

    This is the product description.

    <x-slot name="footer">
        <x-button>Buy Now</x-button>
    </x-slot>
</x-card>

PART 4ï¸âƒ£ â€” CLASS-BASED COMPONENT (More Powerful)
1ï¸âƒ£ Create Component
php artisan make:component Badge


ğŸ“„ Files created:

app/View/Components/Badge.php
resources/views/components/badge.blade.php

2ï¸âƒ£ Component Class

ğŸ“„ Badge.php

namespace App\View\Components;

use Illuminate\View\Component;

class Badge extends Component
{
    public $color;

    public function __construct($color = 'primary')
    {
        $this->color = $color;
    }

    public function render()
    {
        return view('components.badge');
    }
}

3ï¸âƒ£ Blade View

ğŸ“„ badge.blade.php

<span class="badge bg-{{ $color }}">
    {{ $slot }}
</span>

4ï¸âƒ£ Usage
<x-badge color="success">Active</x-badge>
<x-badge color="danger">Inactive</x-badge>

PART 5ï¸âƒ£ â€” ATTRIBUTE MERGING (VERY IMPORTANT ğŸ”¥)
<button {{ $attributes->merge([
    'class' => 'px-4 py-2 rounded bg-blue-500 text-white'
]) }}>
    {{ $slot }}
</button>


Usage:

<x-button class="bg-red-500">
    Delete
</x-button>

